data.title: fat trel Archives
data.text:
Upon his return home from jail – Fat Trel gives an exclusive interview on his time away and to send well wishes to his city! Follow: https://instagram.com/fat_gleesh https://www.instagram.com/littlebaconbear

Brand new heat from the DMV’s own Fat Trel. This is his first Mixtape release since he’s been released from Jail. 17 Dope Tracks, including Slutty Boyz, Rick Ross, Skrilla and more. Check it out.

Dj Gemini sits down with DMV elite, Fat Trel and talk about Finally Free, his situation with MMG, and new projects coming this year.

Welcome Home to The DMV’s Own Fat Trel. Fresh Off of the Wale & Friends concert which featured Trel, Rick Ross, Lightshow and a host of other DMV elite. Fat Fool is back with is brand new visual. Trel also has a brand new mixtape dropping soon.

Finally free with a new perspective, Fat Trel is looking to kick off his 2018 with a hot start. With a new album on the way and some surprises, Fat Gleesh is getting prepared to go up! Watch as Trel shuts down the Bowie State Homecoming stage with some of his classics. WATCH: Fat Trel Talks […]

Shout to Fat Trel who came through to visit Angie Ange and let his fans know that now that he’s out of prison he’s got new music and new perspective on his future…check out the interview!

Welcome Home Fat Gleesh! One of Maybach Music Group’s latest signees, Fat Trel of Washington DC, had fell into legal troubles around April 2016. Serving over a year and some change in an Arlington County jail, last week, Friday September 22nd, the rapper’s manager Debo welcomed the self-proclaimed slutty boy into freedom with open arms, a […]

Fat Trel isn’t a rapper to be marginalized at all! Matter of fact, it seems like every other week he’s exercising his penmanship and wordplay over someone’s industry beats. This month in October the MMG rapper chose to throw his Gleesh-Mix over D.R.A.M.’s “Broccoli” and Will The Rapper’s “Pull Up Hop Out.” As a bonus track, I added one of […]

D.C.’s own Fat Trel is in trouble with the law again. Trel was arrested overnight on Driving While Intoxicated and Narcotics Distribution charges. According to Arlington County Police arrested Trel (real name Martrel Reeves) in the area of I395 North at S. Joyce Street. He was also charged with speeding and driving on a revoked license. In […]

According to TMZ, Fat Trel, was arrested for using counterfeit money in a casino. Trel denies the charges and on Twitter says he doesn’t even own an ATM card.
